    "analysis": "From the previous aggregation step we know metric and trace series cover the incident window (metrics: 31 points covering 2021-03-04 22:00 → 22:30 UTC+8; traces: 30 points covering 22:00 → 22:29 UTC+8). Log and error_log aggregates were empty. Next we must run anomaly detection on metric series (using global thresholds computed from full series) restricted to the incident window. This will narrow down candidate faulty components/KPIs and provide earliest anomaly timestamps and severity for each candidate. Trace and log analysis will follow after metric candidates are found. No concrete anomaly-by-timestamp results have been computed yet.",
